name: Sound of Mourning

description: Look out for more outrageous ramen recipes as Taisho tries every gimmick in the book in order to make his restaurant the most successful cat-run business ever! Not only are there French chefs, curry, fortune-tellers and cooking competitions, but Taisho’s mother comes to visit and let loose Taisho’s most embarrassing secret! What other crazy scheme will Taisho cook up next?
name: Curry is also Delicious!

Kiri Minase's model dad passed on stunning male looks to his only child...unfortunately, Kiri's a girl! Tohya Enishi is the love of her life. In order to protect her Tohya as he enters the world of male modeling, Kiri becomes a male model herself. Things get complicated when others start to fall for Kiri and her male alter ego!

Back Blurb

Kiri's fashion-model dad passed on his stunningly attractive masculine looks to his only child... unfortunately, Kiri is a girl!

Tohya is the love of Kiri's life-- in order to protect him as he enters the world of male modeling, Kiri becomes a male model herself. But things get a bit complicated on the catwalk when others start to fall for Kiri's male alter ego!
name: Vol. 1

description: What is better than a love triangle? How about a love square or rectangle? The action picks up with Kiri trying to clear things up with Tohya and Akira. However, it gets messier than usual. The hot teen idol Makoto Hijiri has taken an interest in Tohya's budding television career. Kiri goes to a modeling shoot, only to be interrupted by Akira and an uninvited guest...
name: Vol. 2

description: As Makoto tries to recruit Akira to help break up Kiri and Tohya, Kiri sinks into a deep depression. When she ends up fainting at school, she's rushed to a clinic, where she gets a visit--and a kiss--from Tohya. But was it all a dream? She better decide fast: Makoto may be on to her, and she's about to find out if Tatsuki and Kiri are really one and the same!
name: Vol. 3

description: Kiri's "transformation" may have been a success, but her secret identity may be more at risk than ever! Enter Yuki, freelance photographer...and extortionist extraordinaire! Now, he's got his camera lens on Kiri, and if she ever hopes of getting out of this in one piece, she'll have to agree to being his newest model!
name: Vol. 4

description: As the photo shoot on Okinawa continues, the prospect of a nude--yes, nude!--photo shoot surfaces, and Akira and Tohya seem none too happy about it. And while Tohya encourages Kiri to be a stronger, more confident model and take chances, Akira tells Tohya to do the same...about a different situation. Will Tohya ever expose his true feelings for Kiri?
name: Vol. 5

description: The training for the fashion show begins! Kiri, Tohya, Akira, Riku, and Kanou start taking lessons together and find out that Mano-sensei is going to give one of them an exclusive contract. Does Kiri have enough swagger to be a fashion model--and will she be able to stay close to the love of her life?
name: Vol. 6

description: Kanou's threat has Kiri on edge, and it doesn't help that she's still struggling with her modeling! Perhaps the story of Kanou's childhood can explain his cold and distant demeanor, and shed new light on their future... But all drama aside, there's still the big night to worry about! Will Kiri nail the show, or walk away from the stage forever?
name: Vol. 7

description: The big fashion show is almost here! With all the troubles that have befallen on Kiri, how will everything turn out? Which lucky model will get the exclusive contract? And most importantly, how will this affect Kiri and Tohya's relationship?! Fate never gives up as whispers of love reveal the biggest surprise of all!
name: Vol. 8

description:
A Sci-Fi Adventure Set in the BLAME! Universe As detective Musubi Susono investigates a series of child kidnappings, her own partner is viciously murdered. But when the investigation takes a brutal turn, she is suddenly confronted by the killer--and his vicious Silicon Creature...

Chapter Titles

  • Chapter 1 - Demonic Invocation
  • Chapter 2 - Assassins
  • Chapter 3 - Net Terminal Implants
  • Chapter 4 - Sacrifice
  • Chapter 5 - Corpse Running Wild
  • Final Chapter - Holy Land
  • Supplemental Chapter - Negative Corridor
  • Four Seasons Chapter - Blame
name: Vol. 1

description:
Meet 15-year-old Tory Blake, a self-proclaimed genius who is somewhat antisocial and more than a bit cynical about the world. Life is just tedious for Tory...until the day an attractive but secretive boy his own age moves in across the street. Tory becomes obsessed by his intriguing new neighbor and begins documenting his every move. But this pursuit of friendship--and possibly something more--leads Tory to the one thing he wasn't expecting to discover.

You like what you've seen so far? Well, you ain't seen nothin' yet! Things are just starting to get interesting for Tory, and his relationship with Colin develops slowly, but surely. Through book one and beyond their friendship deepens as Tory learns more about Colin's past and the mysterious Gaia Project!

Chapter Titles

  • Chapter 1: The Problem
  • Chapter 2: The Investigation
  • Chapter 3: The Contact
  • Chapter 4: The Gaia Project
  • Chapter 5: The Opportunity
  • Chapter 6: The Meeting
name: Vol. 1

description:
Chapter Title 

  • Chapter 7: The Unrequited
  • Chapter 8: The Arrangement
  • Chapter 9: The Unexpected Snowfall
  • Chapter 10: The Resolution
  • Chapter 11: The Indisposition
  • Chapter 12: The Enigmatic
name: Vol. 2

description: Naka is an aspiring young model with a problem: her face tenses up into a terrifying spectacle whenever she gets nervous on photo shoots! Naka's rival is Umi, the hottest model at their agency. But Naka soon discovers Umi's secret--and hilarity ensues behind the cameras!
name: Vol. 1

description: Naka is pleasantly surprised to learn that she's landed another job...but not so pleasantly surprised to learn that Tsutsumi will be the photographer! Meanwhile, Ms. President notices that Umi is starting to look more and more manly, and warns him to be careful. Will everyone learn Umi's secret?
name: Vol. 2

description: Umi and Naka are invited to the grand opening gala for the first Knocks retail store. At the party, Naka spills her drink on the infamous Hideto? Suzuki, the Knocks designer himself! Will this disaster be the final nail in the coffin of her almost dead modeling career?
name: Vol. 3

description: It's been one year since Umi and Naka began modeling for the mega-fashion label, Junk. Mon-mo magazine is going to do a special feature that includes an interview with the models. But now that Naka realizes she's in love with Umi, she has a hard time acting normal around him and messes up the interview, causing it to be postponed. The rest of her work for Junk is being affected as well, and the president of Junk decides it's time for her to go.
name: Vol. 4

description: Everyone continues to vie for Naka's love! Ikue tries his best to make Naka look at him instead of Umi, but when he confesses his feelings for her, she runs away. And Naka herself can't stand seeing the cute Mihane with Umi, which makes her faint in the middle of a shoot! But when Umi kisses her while she's still recovering, will she realize how she truly feels? Find out in this steamy volume of Nosatsu Junkie!
name: Vol. 5

description: Umi knows that he can only pull off posing as a female model for another year at the most, and he wants to make the most of it by modeling for the Heki brand one last time. However, the photographer Ikue has other plans--he wants Naka to be the Heki model! Will work put Umi and Naka's relationship on the rocks again?!
name: Vol. 6

description: Eumpa Won (One) is an awkward, quiet music student and former child prodigy who is now determined to lead his life as a normal guy. Destiny throws him a curve as he finds himself caught up in an unlikely love triangle. Enter Jenny, the highly acclaimed singer, and Young-Ju, the plain Jane. These seemingly opposite personalities are drawn together by two common bonds... Their passion for music and their search for true self-identity.
name: Vol. 1

description: Eumpa turns a deaf ear to the music world, even as Jenny urges him to kick out the jams. But when Eumpa's teacher admits that he stole his student's music, the music industry sings a different tune toward Eumpa. And things just might go from a minor key to a major chord when Jenny's record company turns her into a sexy pop icon. Will the girl gone wild break Eumpa out of his hard rock shell?
name: Vol. 2

description: Now that Jenny has gotten Eumpa's foot into the door of the music world, it's on to auditions! After one small step for the boy and one giant step for boy-band-kind, Eumpa becomes the lead vocalist of the Next One team. But since musical talent isn't in the strength of this new group, Eumpa must learn to set the dance floor ablaze...or be dropped because of his bop.
name: Vol. 3

description: When Jihae Han signs Eumpa's recording contract as his legal guardian, it causes a huge controversy. What's the true nature of their relationship? And will this endanger Eumpa's exploding career? Once again, ONE offers a behind-the-scenes look at the glamorous world of a popstar-in-the-making. If American Idol were a manga, ONE would be it!
name: Vol. 4

description: Scandal rocks the music industry when Jihae reveals the secret about why she dropped out of the scene only to hurl Eumpa's band into the spotlight! As the pop band One tries to make its way to the top, can they cope with their studio's plans to make them famous for being seen rather than heard?
name: Vol. 5

description: Eumpa's strange and unpredictable personality makes him a hit with those around him. After playing matchmaker and a confidant to Yunjin, Eumpa now eyes the top spot on the charts. However fame comes at a steep price as pride, 1 ambitions, and friendships are thrown aside, as told by Sonya. Along his way to stardom, Eumpa vows never to forget his first love, Youngju...but will his loyalty to her rekindle an old flame and spark jealousy in others?
name: Vol. 6

description: Everybody loves Eumpa! On an outing together, Sonia takes a couple of pictures, one of Eumpa with Youngju, and one of Eumpa with Jenny. The next day, splashed across the front page of Music Love is the picture of Eumpa and Jenny, creating a huge scandal! Now Jenny's public image is suffering: Everyone thinks she's a flirt, heartless and cold, and all her fans are turning to Sonia. But is Jenny really the bad guy in all of this, or is it Sonia? And will the truth come out in time to save Jenny's career?
name: Vol. 7

description: Eumpa returns from his first radio interview with TBC, where things didn't go well at all--TBC wouldn't let Eumpa get a word in edgewise! They're building up their national exposure before setting their sites on the top of the charts with an upcoming record release. And as an added slap in the face to Eumpa and his crew, TBC performs their entry for the number one song of the week: "Genocide" by TNT! What will TNT do to beat out this carbon copy of themselves?
name: Vol. 8

description: Eumpa wins the #1 spot but it may not be what he thought. He confronts his manager wondering if the company bought the title from them. With Ha Rock injured, Jenny wrapped in scandal and Sonya involved in a lawsuit, the win sends ripples through management. But all the turmoil is nothing compared to what is going to rock the love lives of Jenny, Eumpa, Ha Rock and Youngju!
name: Vol. 9

description: Woojae is desperate to take Eumpa under his wing, but is Eumpa ready for Woojae's leadership? Meanwhile, Jenny's work performance suffers from her insecurities--can she overcome her slump?
name: Vol. 10

description: The dramatic finale of the scathing critique of the music industry! In the entertainment industry, music is business and inspiration is merely a copy of a copy, so what does it mean to be accused of plagiarism? Eumpa confesses that he ripped off One's smash-hit new single "Jammer" from a German band. The music industry is in an uproar, and the record company wants to patch up the scandal. A press conference may save the band from breaking up--but is that what Eumpa really wants?
name: Vol. 11

description:
Five years ago, a young witch named Cierra broke the one unforgivable law of the witch society: attempting to create her own magic. Her unlawful tampering burned down a research room and injured the Mayor's daughter, Cierra's best friend. As punishment, she was exiled to the Wilderness, a barren wasteland crawling with witch-devouring Fairies and the bloodthirsty Forsaken... After surviving for five ruthless years, her exile has now ended, and she has been ushered back to civilization, only to discover that the world around her has changed greatly. Will Cierra be able to adjust back to a society that abandoned her? And if her freakish new ability that links her to the terrifying Fairies is discovered, she may not be let off with mere exile this time...

Chapter Titles

  • First Scar: Forsaken
  • Second Scar: An Eternity Ago
  • Third Scar: Time Traveler
  • Fourth Scar: Lesser of Two Evils
  • Fifth Scar: Welcome Home
  • Sixth Scar: And All That Is Left
name: Vol. 1

description: For Hikaru, learning swordsmanship is far more interesting than thinking about marriage...and she won't let being the only daughter of a noble house in 10th-century Japan stand in her way! But one fateful day, Hikaru comes across a group of thieves who want revenge on her adored older brother Raikou for obliterating their village. Now Hikaru must sharpen her sword, as she is the only person who can prevent her brother's head from being served on a platter!
name: Vol. 1

description: Seimei gives Karako an ultimatum--he must decide between his own life and Raikou's. To make matters worse, Karako becomes more confused and loses trust in everyone--and Karako stands between Hikaru's escape to freedom...
name: Vol. 2

description: Pamela Baker is not what she seems. On an archeological dig to discover irrefutable evidenace of the existence of werewolves, Pamela finds herself turned into the living proof. She is a werewolf. Unsure of who she is or why she had become this way, the Bloodhound struggles to accept her new identity. And now her saga begins...

volume.name: Secret Files vs Vampire Girls: The Vampire Effect
